title: The Raw Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Raw, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Australian
description: Cafe, smoothie bar, and shop in a warehouse space of exposed brick and rafters. All-raw food and vegan except for honey. Offers raw pizza slices, salads, dessert, coffee, and makes almond milk. Sells products like cacao, goji, and maca powder, seasonings, and books on healthy eating. Hosts yoga and raw food workshops. Relocated from Piazza Arcade.
